        "title": "Operador Arrow",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 103001,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Vamos aprender como criar <strong>arrow functions</strong>. Elas fazem parte do padrão ES6 do JavaScript e são usadas para escrever um código mais limpo e curto.</p><p>Vamos reescrever a função abaixo como uma arrow function usando apenas uma linha de código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hello'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hi'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getGreeting());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"72\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>const greeting = () =&gt; 'Hi';</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Anonymous Function",
            "id": 103846,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Funções arrow são um tipo de <strong>função</strong><strong>anônima</strong>, o que significa que elas não têm um nome de função.</p><p>Se quisermos chamar essas funções, precisamos armazená-las dentro de uma variável e chamar a variável com parênteses no final.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hi'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getGreeting());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"63\" /><option startIndex=\"64\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"131\" endIndex=\"141\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>const greeting</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>greeting()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parentheses",
            "id": 103847,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Com funções de seta, não precisamos da palavra-chave <code>function</code> ou do nome da função. Isso significa que a primeira coisa que começamos é com parênteses.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"68\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parameter",
            "id": 103848,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Assim como com funções normais, podemos adicionar parâmetros dentro dos parênteses e depois usar os parâmetros dentro da função.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"firstName\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + firstName;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"firstName\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + firstName;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting(\" /><text value=\"'Tony'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"));\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"88\" endIndex=\"97\" /><option startIndex=\"127\" endIndex=\"136\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings Tony\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>firstName</code> seguido de <code>firstName</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Arrow operator",
            "id": 103004,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Logo após os parênteses e antes da abertura da chave é onde adicionamos o operador flecha <code>=&gt;</code>.</p><p>Usamos este operador logo antes do bloco de código ou expressão que queremos que a função execute.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" hello = \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"myfunction\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" helloArrowFunction = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(hello());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(helloArrowFunction());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"93\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Greetings \" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Multiple body statements",
            "id": 103005,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Assim como com funções tradicionais, usamos chaves <code>{}</code> para conter o bloco de código de uma arrow function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" name = \" /><text value=\"'Elizabeth'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + name;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>{</code> seguido de <code>};</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "One body statement",
            "id": 103006,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Se uma arrow function tiver apenas uma instrução, podemos deixar de fora tanto as chaves quanto a palavra-chave <code>return</code> para obter um código bem curto.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{ return 'Greetings' }\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>'Greetings'</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Arrow operator",
            "id": 103700,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Onde adicionamos o operador de seta <code>=&gt;</code>?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Após os parênteses e antes da abertura da chave</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Após a palavra-chave <code>function</code> e antes da chave de abertura <code>{</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Após os parênteses e antes da abertura da chave.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Multiple body statements",
            "id": 103701,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O que as chaves <code>{}</code> fazem em uma arrow function?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Eles contêm o bloco de código</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Eles são usados para chamar uma função</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Eles contêm o bloco de código.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: One body statement",
            "id": 103702,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como podemos encurtar o seguinte código?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Removendo as chaves <code>{}</code> e a palavra-chave <code>return</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Removendo os parênteses <code>()</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Removendo as chaves <code>{}</code> e a palavra-chave <code>return</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Calling the function",
            "id": 103704,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como chamamos a seguinte função de seta?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" position = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello Jane!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>greetings();</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>greetings;</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>greetings();</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Parenthesis",
            "id": 103706,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Complete a função de seta.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehicleCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count = \" /><text value=\"4003\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehicleCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"26\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"var\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4003\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Arrow operator",
            "id": 103707,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifique o operador de seta, <code>=&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehiclesCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count = \" /><text value=\"4003\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehiclesCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4003\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: One body statement",
            "id": 103709,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Faça a função retornar o valor <code>400</code> escrevendo a função arrow mais curta possível.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehiclesCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"400\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehiclesCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"return\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"400\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>()</code> seguido de <code>=&gt;</code> e finalmente <code>400</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Calling the function",
            "id": 103711,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Chame a arrow function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getMessage = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to Cyprus!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getMessage());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"59\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"69\" endIndex=\"70\" /><option startIndex=\"70\" endIndex=\"71\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Welcome to Cyprus!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>getMessage</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
